;;;
;;; Methods themselves are simple inanimate objects.  Most properties of
;;; methods are immutable, methods cannot be reinitialized.  The following
;;; properties of methods can be changed:
;;;   METHOD-GENERIC-FUNCTION
;;;   METHOD-FUNCTION            ??
